Package: cytokineFindeR
Title: Measure ligands of interest (cytokines) across different methods and databases
Version: 0.0.1.9001
Authors@R: 
    person("Jeffrey", "Tang", , "jeffrey.tang@hli.ubc.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5633-6123"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for measuring and analyzing cytokines and 
    other ligands of interest across multiple analytical methods and biological 
    databases. Provides functions for data retrieval, statistical analysis, 
    and visualization of cytokine expression patterns using pre-defined 
    ligand-receptor interactions.
